Day 19 - 427*
It looks like the girl has down syndrome. Other than being funny doesn't have anything that stands out, the art is mediocre at best and even if she is a prodigy, a child would not be hired by a school. That's all that I have to say, also, for a prodigy, she didn't seem to know much about her own body.
Overall not bad but I won't come back to this.
3/10.
Got a good laugh but that's it 5/10
